# KVM/QEMU hypervisors to enumerate VMs from.
# One hostname per line. Lines starting with # are ignored.
# The inventory generator connects to each hypervisor via SSH and
# lists all libvirt domains to build the dynamic inventory.
#
# Copy this file to hypervisors.txt and add your hypervisor hostnames:
#   cp hypervisors.txt.example hypervisors.txt
#
# Example:
#   hypervisor1
#   hypervisor2.example.local
